---

---

<section
  id="about"
  class="py-32 dark:bg-gray-900 transition-colors justify-center items-center flex min-h-screen m-4 p-4"
  style="background-color:var(--color-warm-white);"
>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="reveal-section grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Image column -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div
          class="absolute -top-10 -left-10 w-40 h-40 rounded-full opacity-40 blur-3xl"
          style="background:var(--color-coral-light);"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 w-48 h-48 rounded-full opacity-30 blur-3xl"
          style="background:var(--color-gold-light);"
        >
        </div>

        <div
          class="relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl"
          style="aspect-ratio:3/4;"
        >
          <img
            src="https://ext.same-assets.com/94436006/1303403810.png"
            alt="Maria Isabel Begueri — Hospitality Professional"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            fetchpriority="low"
            width="600"
            height="800"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0"
            style="background:linear-gradient(to top, rgba(224,122,95,0.15), transparent);"
          >
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Floating card: Experience -->
        <div
          class="glass absolute right-2 md:-right-10 top-1/4 rounded-2xl p-4 shadow-xl animate-float flex flex-col items-center gap-1"
          style="animation-delay:0s;"
        >
          <p
            class="text-3xl font-bold items-center"
            style="color:var(--color-coral);"
          >
            15+
          </p>
          <p
            class="text-sm font-medium mt-0.5 lang-text px-2 text-center"
            style="color:var(--color-charcoal);"
            data-en="Years Experience"
            data-sv="Års Erfarenhet"
          >
            Years Experience
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Floating card: Languages -->
        <div
          class="glass absolute left-2 md:-left-10 bottom-1/4 rounded-2xl p-4 shadow-xl animate-float flex flex-col items-center gap-1"
          style="animation-delay:0.8s;"
        >
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold" style="color:var(--color-gold);">5+</p>
          <p
            class="text-sm font-medium mt-0.5 lang-text px-2 text-center"
            style="color:var(--color-charcoal);"
            data-en="Languages"
            data-sv="Språk"
          >
            Languages
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text column -->
      <div class="space-y-6 h-full flex flex-col justify-center gap-6">
        <p
          class="section-subtitle lang-text"
          data-en="Let me introduce myself"
          data-sv="Låt mig presentera mig"
        >
          Let me introduce myself
        </p>
        <h2
          class="section-title dark:text-white lang-text"
          data-en="More Than a Receptionist"
          data-sv="Mer Än En Receptionist"
        >
          More Than a Receptionist
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-5 mt-6">
          <p
            class="text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed dark:text-gray-300 lang-text"
            style="color:var(--color-charcoal-light);"
            data-en="I believe that every interaction is an opportunity to create a meaningful connection. With over 15 years in hospitality and customer service, I've learned that the key to excellence isn't just what you do — it's how you make people feel."
            data-sv="Jag tror att varje interaktion är en möjlighet att skapa en meningsfull koppling. Med över 15 års erfarenhet inom gästfrihet och kundservice har jag lärt mig att nyckeln till excellens inte bara är vad du gör — det är hur du får människor att känna sig."
          >
            I believe that every interaction is an opportunity to create a
            meaningful connection. With over 15 years in hospitality and
            customer service, I've learned that the key to excellence isn't just
            what you do — it's how you make people feel.
          </p>
          <p
            class="text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed dark:text-gray-300 lang-text"
            style="color:var(--color-charcoal-light);"
            data-en="I'm a curious learner, a natural problem-solver, and someone who finds genuine joy in helping others. Whether it's welcoming guests to a hotel, managing car rental reservations, or supporting a team, I bring warmth, efficiency, and a smile to everything I do."
            data-sv="Jag är en nyfiken lärare, en naturlig problemlösare och någon som finner äkta glädje i att hjälpa andra. Oavsett om det handlar om att välkomna gäster till ett hotell, hantera biluthyrningsreservationer eller stödja ett team, går jag in med värme, effektivitet och ett leende i allt jag gör."
          >
            I'm a curious learner, a natural problem-solver, and someone who
            finds genuine joy in helping others.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Values grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"
              style="background:var(--color-coral-light);"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5"
                style="color:var(--color-coral-dark);"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span
              class="font-semibold text-sm dark:text-gray-200 lang-text"
              style="color:var(--color-charcoal);"
              data-en="Empathetic"
              data-sv="Empatisk">Empathetic</span
            >
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"
              style="background:var(--color-gold-light);"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5"
                style="color:var(--color-terracotta);"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span
              class="font-semibold text-sm dark:text-gray-200 lang-text"
              style="color:var(--color-charcoal);"
              data-en="Proactive"
              data-sv="Proaktiv">Proactive</span
            >
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"
              style="background:rgba(139,157,131,0.2);"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5"
                style="color:var(--color-sage);"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span
              class="font-semibold text-sm dark:text-gray-200 lang-text"
              style="color:var(--color-charcoal);"
              data-en="Team Player"
              data-sv="Lagspelåre">Team Player</span
            >
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"
              style="background:var(--color-rose-light);"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5"
                style="color:var(--color-terracotta);"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span
              class="font-semibold text-sm dark:text-gray-200 lang-text"
              style="color:var(--color-charcoal);"
              data-en="Detail-Oriented"
              data-sv="Detaljorienterad">Detail-Oriented</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
